title: Amazon Fires co-hashtag network
description: We collected Twitter data covering the period of 24th August to 2nd September 2019 (10 days) using the following hashtags: #ActForTheAmazon, #amazonfires, #AmazonRainforest, #PrayforAmazonia, #SaveTheAmazon, and #SOSAmazonia.
